<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Meta tags for character set, viewport, and CSRF token -->
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <!-- CSRF token for security -->
    <meta name="csrf-token" content="<%= csrfToken %>" />
    <!-- Title of the Learning Management System -->
    <title>Learning Management System - Empowering Education</title>
    <!-- CSS styling for the page -->
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #e0e0e0;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Main content container -->
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Introduction paragraph about the Learning Management System -->
      <p>
        Welcome to our Learning Management System (LMS), designed to empower
        educators and students alike. Utilizing cutting-edge technologies such
        as Node.js, Express.js, Sequelize, and Passport.js, our platform
        delivers a robust authentication system ensuring secure access for all
        users.
      </p>
      <!-- Additional details about user-friendliness -->
      <p>
        Our LMS prioritizes user-friendliness, allowing seamless password
        updates and convenient sign-out options from any location. These
        features are tailored to enhance the user experience, promoting
        effortless interaction and engagement with the platform.
      </p>
      <!-- Importance of security, reliability, and tracking progress -->
      <p>
        Security and reliability are fundamental pillars of our system,
        guaranteeing a safe and dependable learning environment. Furthermore,
        progress-tracking features facilitate goal achievement and ensure
        optimal learning outcomes for every user.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
